The paper presents a fast oblivious L2-embedding with applications to machine learning tasks such as regression and PCA, indicating a focus on the field of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses statistical leverage scores, which falls under the category of numerical analysis (cs.NA). The use of embeddings and dimensionality reduction suggests a potential connection to information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI). Finally, the paper also presents an application to L1 tasks, indicating a potential connection to data structures (cs.DS) for efficient computation of L1-embeddings.
